        <h2 class="text-3xl">Selected Hotels</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-xl mb-4">We have visited and inspected a number of hotels in the direct vicinity of the Brewery - we looked at rooms in each one and have selected three that we believe represent excellent value for conference accommodation. There are many other hotels in the area including, of course, the Montcalm which is located in the conference centre.</p>
